OL,3,CManchester United's billion-pound
OL,4,Csquad breaks UEFA record
OL,6,F's squad at the end of last season was
OL,7,Fthe most expensively-assembled on
OL,8,Frecord, according to a UEFA report.
OL,10,FThe Red Devils' squad at 2023's
OL,11,Ffinancial year-end cost a collective
OL,12,F1.42 billion euros (#1.21bn) in
OL,13,Ftransfer fees, eclipsing the figure of
OL,14,F1.33 billion euros recorded by Real
OL,15,FMadrid in 2020.
OL,17,FThe United squad at the end of 2022-23
OL,18,Fincluded #82million Brazilian winger
OL,19,FAntony, #80m England defender Harry
OL,20,FMaguire, #73m signing Jadon Sancho and
OL,21,Fthe #60m Brazil midfielder Casemiro.
