OL,3,CManchester United's billion-pound
OL,4,Csquad breaks UEFA record
OL,6,FChelsea's most recent figures go up to
OL,7,Fthe year end June 30, 2022, and
OL,8,Ftherefore do not include their heavy
OL,9,Fspending in the summer of that year or
OL,10,Fthe January 2023 window.
OL,12,FUnited have become one of 15 English
OL,13,Ftop-flight clubs recognised within the
OL,14,Freport as being part of a multi-club
OL,15,Finvestment group, with the purchase of
OL,16,Fa 25% stake by Ineos founder Sir Jim
OL,17,FRatcliffe almost complete.
OL,19,FIneos also holds majority stakes in
OL,20,FFrench side Nice and Swiss club
OL,21,FLausanne.
