OL,3,CManchester United's billion-pound
OL,4,Csquad breaks UEFA record
OL,6,FIn all, 105 top-division European
OL,7,Fclubs (13% of the total number) have a
OL,8,Fcross-investment relationship with one
OL,9,For more other clubs, the report found.
OL,11,FThere were 31 purchases of majority
OL,12,Fstakes and seven purchases of minority
OL,13,Fstakes in 2023 by groups holding a
OL,14,Fstake in at least one other European
OL,15,Fclub, according to the report.
OL,17,FHowever, less than one transfer per
OL,18,Fclub on average is actually executed
OL,19,Fwithin the same multi-club structure,
OL,20,Fthe report found.
