OL,6,FAndrea Traverso, UEFA's director of
OL,7,Ffinancial sustainability and research,
OL,8,Fsaid: "More than 300 clubs are part of
OL,9,Fmulti-club investment groups, leading
OL,10,Fto an increased risk of seeing two
OL,11,Fclubs with the same owner or investor
OL,12,Ffacing each other in the same
OL,13,Fcompetition, creating potential
OL,14,Fintegrity risks at the European level.
