OL,3,CManchester United's billion-pound
OL,4,Csquad breaks UEFA record
OL,6,F"The current context demands strict
OL,7,Fenforcement of cost control
OL,8,Fregulations and more harmonisation of
OL,9,Ffinancial rules between leagues. This
OL,10,Fis paramount to limit overspending,
OL,11,F'creative finance', and rules
OL,12,Fcircumvention.
OL,14,F"As long as differences on key
OL,15,Fregulatory matters continue between
OL,16,Fleagues, inflationary tensions will
OL,17,Fpersist, contributing to imbalances
OL,18,Fand instability."
