OL,6,FElsewhere, the report found spending
OL,7,Fon player wages dropped by 1.1 per
OL,8,Fcent among the clubs with the 20
OL,9,Flargest player wage bills, with United
OL,10,Fspending 88m euros (#75m) less on
OL,11,Fplayer wages in 2023 compared to the
OL,12,Fyear before. Barcelona and City had
OL,13,Flarge increases in player wages
OL,14,Fspending ` 158m euros and 68m euros
OL,15,F(#134.8m and #58m) respectively.
